    <description>First of all, I&#39;m not saying the cult needs buffs. I think cult is fine balance wise, however it is too similar to the unseen. Sacrifice which should be the cult&#39;s main thing is almost never used currently. So my suggestion is that whenever you use sacrifice you not only give cult leader extra eradicate charges but also give extra uses to all other cultists&#39; limited abilities. Of course, the number of uses of each ability should be tweaked to avoid this from being a direct buff.</description>
    
