      <item>
        <title>Cult sacrifice changes</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[UncannyLuck]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Yeah but you’re giving up a cult member is the problem, and you can lose out on it anyway through any number of ways (random CS, dies to bleeding, prince exe). So even if you want to use it strategically, for example have a cult member accuse someone and get them exe’d on trial and then you sac them that night, you can’t really.</p>
<p>If it just refreshed the CD of Brainwash it’d probably be used all the time. It’d also likely be broken.</p>
          <p><a href="https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/cult-sacrifice-changes/55925/10">Read full topic</a></p>
        ]]></description>
